snippet.title: Finally, in Love Again - Opening Movie
snippet.description:
Finally, in Love Again

For my birthday, I got...
Love for the first time in 10 years!?

You're a pastry chef. Wrapped up in your job, your love life has fallen by the wayside.
When you go to a singles event on your birthday, five attractive men profess their love for you!

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

★Love 365 at the App Store★
https://itunes.apple.com/jp/app/love-365-find-your-story/id1266172764?mt=8

★Love 365 at Google Play★
